@startuml
!include ../includes/appsec-style.puml
title AppSec Process 01: Application Onboarding & Coverage Plan

' Purpose: Classify the application (SaaS/COTS/Homegrown + install type) and produce a
'          tool-backed security testing plan with clear ownership and a unique Application Code (AppCode).

start

partition "Intake" {
  :Request received;
  :Collect metadata (name, repo/vendor, environments);
  :Assign/verify **Application Code (AppCode)**;
  :Identify business + technical owner;
  :Record AppCode in app inventory / CMDB;
}

partition "Classify" {
  if (App type?) then (Homegrown)
    :Repo + CI mapped (tag repo/pipeline with AppCode);
    :Language inventory;
    :Enable SonarQube project (key = AppCode);
    if (CodeQL coverage?) then (Yes)
      :Enable GHAS SAST (CodeQL) for AppCode;
    else (No)
      :Enable Coverity (gap SAST) for AppCode;
    endif
    :Enable GHAS secrets (AppCode scope);
    :Enable GHAS SCA/Dependabot (AppCode scope);
    :Plan Trivy scans (IaC + containers);
  elseif (COTS)
    :Product + version (AppCode);
    :Patch channel + update cadence;
    :Support contract + escalation path;
    :Define vendor disclosure intake (CVE advisories);
  else (SaaS)
    :Vendor + service (AppCode);
    :Tenant model + data classification;
    :Integration scope (APIs, SSO, SCIM);
    :Define vendor assurance artifacts (SOC2/ISO, pen test);
  endif
}

partition "Install Model" {
  if (Install type?) then (Cloud)
    :Select scanning environments;
  elseif (Hybrid)
    :Select scanning environments;
  elseif (On Premise)
    :Select scanning environments;
  elseif (Third-party hosted)
    :Select scanning environments;
  else (Service subscription)
    :Select scanning environments;
  endif
}

partition "Coverage Plan" {
  :Define required gates (by risk tier);
  :Select IAST (Seeker) targets (AppCode);
  :Select DAST (InsightAppSec) targets (AppCode);
  :Define scan cadence + reporting;
  :Define ownership routing (AppCode -> team);
  :Create baseline record + compliance status;
}

note right
Key message: **Every application has an AppCode, an owner, and a coverage plan**
based on app type + install model.
end note

stop
@enduml
